# Autocommit opt-in marker (Claude Process Standards Rule 5, SOP rev4+).
#
# The presence of this file opts leka-product-catalogs INTO the Stop-hook
# automation in scripts/auto-commit-and-merge.sh: after a turn that edits code
# and passes verify.sh, Claude auto-commits, pushes, waits on the CI gate
# (scripts/check-ci-status.sh), and admin-squash-merges feature-branch PRs only
# when CI is green. Collaborator PRs still require CODEOWNERS review (Rule 11).
#
# Opt OUT per-turn by saying "draft only" / "don't push" / "don't commit" /
# "hold off". Remove this file to opt the whole project back out.
#
# Enabled: 2026-05-29 (by user request).
